{"tid":2260143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金管局：預先批核還息不還本計劃已批出5900億元","createTime":"2020-10-27T10:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T12:21:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3c461aea7c96bf3e1e5b86b0c61fc2173e426b3b","tid":2260143,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:58:39.000Z","msg":"金管局：預先批核還息不還本計劃已批出5900億元<br />\n<br />\n金管局總裁余偉文在匯思撰文指，中小企是香港經濟重要支柱，佔香港企業總數逾98%，佔私營機構總就業人數約45%。過去數月，金管局與銀行積極協調，銀行為企業持續提供貸款，以渡過難關。<br />\n<br />\n至9月底，「預先批核還息不還本」計劃及其他支援企業客戶措施，已批出約4.9萬宗，涉及約5900億港元。<br />\n<br />\n至於中小企融資擔保計劃下，八成及九成信貸擔保產品，首9個月共批出3700宗申請，金額約110億元。<br />\n<br />\n百分百擔保特惠貸款自推出以來，已為逾萬家企業提供超過270億元貸款。<br />\n<br />\n余偉文指，這些均是非常時期非常措施，在確保銀行體系穩健的前提下，金管局將不時檢討各項措施的延長方案，並要思考如何長遠改善中小企借貸環境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556924-20201027.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556924-20201027.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=c8852b0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556924-20201027.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4ee3f318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556924-20201027.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b6c519bbc7b24fd7716005a2853128ef2829b1fb","tid":2260143,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"有幾多攞左去抽拍x莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944990e051ff1ce2c06580caa723650b93caf9b2","tid":2260143,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"HKMA有幾多個5900億?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e639b61c446a1b3bc77669f2d6adc2c6b84bff54","tid":2260143,"uid":289708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-1